    "html": "<h1>Production</h1>\n<p>Work centers and work orders, run from the shop floor on a phone: big touch targets, shift views, and offline tolerance — actions taken without signal queue up and sync when you&#39;re back, with a clear record of what happened.</p>\n<p><em>This chapter is written when the feature ships (roadmap Phase 6). Planned pages:</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Work a shift from your phone, including offline (member)</li>\n<li>Run your team&#39;s orders (team-manager)</li>\n<li>Set up work centers (company-admin)</li>\n</ul>\n"
