    "html": "<h1>Training</h1>\n<p>Courses, certifications and mandatory training, linked to HR records: who needs what, who&#39;s certified, what expires when — with reminders before certifications lapse.</p>\n<p><em>This chapter is written when the feature ships (roadmap: after the core modules). Planned pages:</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li>My courses &amp; certificates (member)</li>\n<li>Assign and track training (team-manager)</li>\n<li>Mandatory training &amp; compliance reports (company-admin)</li>\n</ul>\n"
